                "invention-title": [
                    "Salt-tolerant high-efficiency phenol degradation thermophilic bacterium and application thereof",
                    "一株耐盐高效苯酚降解高温菌及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a salt-tolerant high-efficiency phenol degradation thermophilic bacterium and application thereof, the salt-tolerant high-efficiency phenol degradation thermophilic bacterium is named as W-12 and is identified as Aeribacillus pallidus; the strain W-12 can normally grow under the conditions that the pH value is 6.0-9.0, the temperature is 45-65 DEG C and the NaCl concentration is 1.0-9.0% (w/v), and has better salt tolerance; the strain W-12 can efficiently degrade phenolic substances, such as 500-1,900 mg/L phenol, and can grow and degrade phenol by taking 1,000 mg/L phenol as the only carbon source and energy in the range of pH (potential of hydrogen) of 6.0-9.0 and temperature of 45-65 DEG C; a further research on the strain shows that the strain shows high salt adaptability under low-concentration phenol and shows medium salt tolerance under high-concentration phenol, and the wide adaptability shows that the strain has potential application value in bioremediation of various types of actual phenol-containing wastewater."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种耐盐高效苯酚降解高温菌及其应用，命名为W‑12，鉴定为Aeribacillus pallidus；菌株W‑12能够在pH值6.0‑9.0、温度45‑65℃、NaCl浓度1.0‑9.0％(w/v)范围内正常生长，具有较佳的耐盐能力；菌株W‑12能够高效降解酚类物质，如能够高效降解500‑1,900mg/L的苯酚，在pH＝6.0‑9.0、温度45‑65℃范围内能以1,000mg/L苯酚为唯一碳源和能源生长并降解苯酚；通过对该菌株的进一步研究，发现其在低浓度苯酚下表现高盐适应性，在高浓度苯酚下表现出中盐耐受性，广泛适应性表明其在生物修复多种类型的实际含酚废水中的潜在应用价值。"
                }
            ]
